title: Run C&W
description:
run c&w is a country project that only made 2 albums.  The 4 group members crashen burns, wash burns, side burns, rug burns convert vintage soul music into bluegrass.  the real group consists of ex-eagle Bernie Leadon, ex-amazing rythm ace russel smith and nashville songwriters Vince melamed and Jim photoglo.  the first album released 1993 Into the twngy 21st Century and the second album Row vs. Wade released 1995.  the songson row vs wade are:
1. Let me in
2.medley:hotcorn, coldcorn I like it like that
3. reach out i'll be there
4. hold what you've got
5. signed sealed delivered (i'm yours)
6. papa was a rolling stone
7. spanish harlem
8. i second that emotion
9. chain of fools
10. bring it on home to me

the songs on the other album are in the file, this is my first upload so i hope it works and i hope you like it, it is GOOD!
